SS安装，主题的操作等问题。','Visit the Knowledge Base'=>'访问智库','Read More About the Pro Theme'=>'查阅更多关于专业版的信息','View Premium Version'=>'查看专业版','Need help with using the WordPress as quickly as possible? Visit our well-organized Knowledge Base!'=>'想快速入门使用WORDPRESS？请访问我们井井有条的智库！','You will also get more frequent updates and quicker support with the Pro version.'=>'购买专业版可获得更加频繁的更新以及更加快速高效的售后帮助。','Below is a list of recommended plugins to install that will help you get the most out of %1$s. Although each plugin is optional, it is recommended that you at least install the BlossomThemes Toolkit, BlossomThemes Email Newsletter & BlossomThemes Social Feed to create a website similar to the %1$s demo.'=>'下方罗列着一些我们推荐安装的插件，可让你在使用%1$s的时候得到更精彩的体验。虽然每一个插件都是可选的，然而如果你想创作一个近似%1$s演示的网站，我们推荐你至少要安装花团主题工具箱、花团主题电邮简报以及花团主题社交媒体插件。','Also, you might experience a slower response time during the weekend, so please bear with us.'=>'另外，周末期间的回复时间可能会慢些，请多多包涵。','New to the WordPress world? Our documentation has step by step procedure to create a beautiful website.'=>'刚加入WORDPRESS的世界？我们的使用说明文件会教你如何一步一步打造精美的网站。','How can I solve my issues quickly and get faster support?'=>'怎么能更快解决我的问题，得到帮助？','If this didn\'t help, please %1$scontact us%2$s.'=>'如果这样没有解决问题，请 %1$s联系我们%2$s。','When you submit the support ticket, please try to provide as much details as possible so that we can solve your problem faster. We recommend you to send us a screenshot(s) with issues explained and your website\'s address (URL).'=>'提交客服号时，请尽可能地详细介绍问题，以便我们迅速为您解决。我们建议你为我们提供截屏、所出现的问题以及域名信息（URL）。','Before you send us a support ticket for any issues, please make sure you have updated the theme to the latest version. We might have fixed the bug in the theme update.'=>'无论任何问题，请你提交客服号之前先确认自己用的是主题的最新版本。我们可能在新版本里已经解决该问题了。','Why is my theme not working well?'=>'为什么我的主题不好用了？','What are the advantages of upgrading to the Premium version?'=>'升级付费版本有哪些好处？','Upgrading to the Pro version- will I lose my changes?'=>'升级专业版会不会丢失以前的更改？','How do I change the copyright text?'=>'怎么修改版权文本？','If the Knowledge Base didn\'t answer your queries, submit us a support ticket here. Our response time usually is less than a business day, except on the weekends.'=>'如果你在智库里找不到问题的答案，请在这里提交客服申请。周末之外，一般情况下我们回复你的时间不会超过一个工作日。','It\'s always a good idea to visit our %1$sKnowledge Base%2$s before you send us a support ticket.'=>'向我们提交客服申请之前，最好先访问一下我们的%1$s智库%2$s。','If your customizer is not loading properly or you are having issues with the theme, it might be due to the plugin conflict.'=>'如果个性化设置没有办法加载，或是你在使用主题的过程中遇到麻烦，可能存在插件不兼容的问题。','The Pro version is built with lots of flexibility in mind for future upgrades. Therefore, it is slightly different than the free theme but extremely flexible and easy-to-use.'=>'由于将来专业版本的更新频率会比免费版本更高，它会与免费版本存在一些细微的区别，但是它非常灵活，易于使用。','However, since the Pro version comes with added features and settings, you will need to set up the additional features in the customizer. This process is simple and only takes a few minutes.'=>'然而，由于专业版拥有更多功能以及设置，你必须在个性化设置里设置这些附加功能。整个操作过程非常简单，仅需几分钟。','Overall, you will have more control over your website with the Pro version. You can find out more about the difference between Free and Pro versions 
